main event: A witness reported seeing a single oval-shaped, silver, and slightly cigar-shaped object in the sky.
interesting points: The object was the size of a basketball held at arm's length.
The object had a white flickering color with a radish greenish sparkling appearance.
The object trailed to the left side, about half the size of the main object.
The object gradually faded and disappeared over the course of 15 minutes.
sighted object: single oval-shaped, silver, slightly cigar-shaped object
